WEBVTT

00:00:00.569 --> 00:00:03.113
Ime mi je McKenna Pope.
Stara sem 14 let.

00:00:03.113 --> 00:00:05.102
Ko sem bila stara 13, sem prepričala

00:00:05.102 --> 00:00:06.832
enega največjih proizvajalcev igrač

00:00:06.832 --> 00:00:09.235
na svetu, Hasbro,

00:00:09.235 --> 00:00:11.193
da so spremenili način oglaševanja

00:00:11.193 --> 00:00:13.319
svojih najbolje prodajanih izdelkov.

00:00:13.319 --> 00:00:14.639
O tem vam bom govorila.

00:00:14.639 --> 00:00:16.456
Imam brata, Gavina.

00:00:16.456 --> 00:00:18.875
Ko se je vse to zgodilo, 
je bil star štiri leta.

00:00:18.875 --> 00:00:20.388
Rad je kuhal.

00:00:20.388 --> 00:00:22.606
Neprestano je hodil 
po sestavine v hladilnik

00:00:22.606 --> 00:00:24.746
in jih zamešal v seveda

00:00:24.746 --> 00:00:26.135
neužitne jedi

00:00:26.135 --> 00:00:29.176
ali pa je skuhal nevidne makarone s sirom.

00:00:29.176 --> 00:00:32.325
Zares si je želel postati kuhar.